IMAPStore self-imap
Host imap.gmail.com
User self@sungpae.com
Port 993
UseIMAPS yes
RequireSSL yes
CertificateFile ~/.certificates/gmail.crt
#Pass <%= %x(pass google.com/self@sungpae.com).chomp.inspect %>
#GPGPassFile ~/.password-store/google.com/self@sungpae.com.gpg

IMAPStore gmail-imap
Host imap.gmail.com
User sungpae@gmail.com
Port 993
UseIMAPS yes
RequireSSL yes
CertificateFile ~/.certificates/gmail.crt
#GPGPassFile ~/.password-store/google.com/sungpae@gmail.com-ephemeral1-iphone.gpg

MaildirStore self-mdir
Path ~/Mail/self/
Inbox ~/Mail/INBOX
Flatten .

MaildirStore gmail-mdir
Path ~/Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel self
Master :self-imap:
Slave :self-mdir:
Patterns *
Sync All
Create Slave
Expunge Both

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-imap:
Slave :gmail-mdir:
Patterns *
Sync All
Create Slave
Expunge Both
